Summary: Speed Dreams : An Open Motorsport Sim - DATA
Name: speed-dreams-data
Version: @VERSION@
Release: mkrel2
Epoch: 1
Source: speed-dreams-%{version}-data.tgz
Group: Amusements/Games
BuildRoot: %{_tmppath}/%{name}-buildroot
Copyright: GPL
BuildArch: noarch
URL: http://speed-dreams.sourceforge.net
